{"name":"Sorcerous Origin feature","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>At 6th level, you gain a feature granted by your Sorcerous Origin.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Sorcerer 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"classFeature","source":"PHB","hash":"sorcerous%20origin%20feature_sorcerer_phb_6_phb","propDroppable":"classFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"4dfd0ce30af5100402e4454fd28dc2aa5172ac31"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682005705299,"modifiedTime":1682005705299,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"Qlq79v399z9Xrm85"}
{"name":"Psychic Mirror","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>At 14th level, you gain the ability to shield your mind and redirect psychic energies to the creatures around you. You can't be targeted by any divination magic or perceived through magical scrying sensors.</p><p>Additionally, when you take psychic damage, you can use your reaction to spend one sorcery point to negate the damage, and each creature within 5 feet of you must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw against your sorcerer spell save DC or take psychic damage equal to the damage negated.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ATLAS","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":"when you take psychic damage, you can use"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Sorcerer 14 (Star Spawn (ATLAS))","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"adnd5e":{"itemInfo":{"type":"reaction"}},"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"ATLAS","hash":"psychic%20mirror_sorcerer_phb_star%20spawn%20(atlas)_atlas_14_atlas","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"6544acf47a533cf19f27dff4f211c81cc0788e43"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682005697180,"modifiedTime":1682005697180,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"RSasvMSZjIcnj6hG"}
{"name":"Stygian Inhalation","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>At 10th level, you can inhale the deathly vapors let off by living creatures as they pass. When a living creature within 30 feet of you dies, you can use your reaction to gain temporary hit points equal to twice your level in this class. While you have temporary hit points granted by this feature, wisps of black smoke escape your mouth when you speak and you have resistance to nonmagical damage. Once you use this feature, you must finish a short or long rest before you can use it again.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"BH:SP","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":"When a living creature within 30 feet of you dies, you can use"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"sr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Spiritualist 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"adnd5e":{"itemInfo":{"type":"reaction"}},"plutonium":{"page":"classFeature","source":"BH:SP","hash":"stygian%20inhalation_spiritualist_bh%3asp_10_bh%3asp","propDroppable":"classFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"6b4425581eeb3d29d1d47bec4b4063a4a5cf6c9f"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682005703113,"modifiedTime":1682005703113,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"STpZw8TJzL6OcTvX"}
{"name":"Out of Phase","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>Starting at 1st level, you gain the ability to move through material space. You can use a bonus action on your turn to become partially ethereal. Until the end of your turn, you can move through creatures and objects as if they were difficult terrain. Each creature you move through takes [[/r 1d10]] psychic damage; no creature can take this damage more than once per turn. You take [[/r 1d10]] psychic damage if you end your turn inside an object and you are immediately shunted to the nearest unoccupied space that you can occupy.</p><p>You can use this feature a number of times equal to your Charisma modifier (a minimum of once). You regain all expended uses when you finish a short or long rest.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ATLAS","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"sr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d10","psychic"],["1d10","psychic"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Sorcerer 1 (Star Spawn (ATLAS))","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"ATLAS","hash":"out%20of%20phase_sorcerer_phb_star%20spawn%20(atlas)_atlas_1_atlas","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"72efe8c17e143337cc6d074b2769ee0861751e57"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682005697024,"modifiedTime":1682005697024,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"ShnHSf2BiSyvBcXE"}
{"name":"Storm's Fury","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>Starting at 14th level, when you are hit by a melee attack, you can use your reaction to deal lightning damage to the attacker. The damage equals your sorcerer level. The attacker must also make a Strength saving throw against your sorcerer spell save DC. On a failed save, the attacker is pushed in a straight line up to 20 feet away from you.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":"when you are hit by a melee attack, you can use"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"str","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Sorcerer 14 (Storm)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"adnd5e":{"itemInfo":{"type":"reaction"}},"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"XGE","hash":"storm's%20fury_sorcerer_phb_storm_xge_14_xge","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"6d078dd78306b90455da9f717934a9f4a39648d8"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682005702081,"modifiedTime":1682005702081,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"T6oiEK2mKUVhBV64"}
{"name":"Wild Magic Surge","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>Starting when you choose this origin at 1st level, your spellcasting can unleash surges of untamed magic. Immediately after you cast a sorcerer spell of 1st level or higher, the DM can have you roll a [[/r d20]]. If you roll a 1, roll on the Wild Magic Surge table to create a random magical effect. A Wild Magic Surge can happen once per turn.</p><p>If a Wild Magic effect is a spell, it's too wild to be affected by Metamagic. If it normally requires concentration, it doesn't require concentration in this case; the spell lasts for its full duration.</p><table class=\"w-100 rd__table  stripe-odd-table\"><caption>Wild Magic Surge</caption><thead><tr><th class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-rd-isroller=\"true\">[[/r d100]]</th><th class=\"col-11\" data-rd-isroller=\"false\">Effect</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"1\" data-roll-max=\"2\">01-02</td><td class=\"col-11\">Roll on this table at the start of each of your turns for the next minute, ignoring this result on subsequent rolls.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"3\" data-roll-max=\"4\">03-04</td><td class=\"col-11\">For the next minute, you can see any @condition[invisible] creature if you have line of sight to it.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"5\" data-roll-max=\"6\">05-06</td><td class=\"col-11\">A <a href=\"https://5etools-mirror-1.github.io/bestiary.html#blankhash,flstsource:mm=1,fbsr:modron\">modron</a> chosen and controlled by the DM appears in an unoccupied space within 5 feet of you, then disappears 1 minute later.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"7\" data-roll-max=\"8\">07-08</td><td class=\"col-11\">You cast @spell[fireball] as a 3rd-level spell centered on yourself.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"9\" data-roll-max=\"10\">09-10</td><td class=\"col-11\">You cast @spell[magic missile] as a 5th-level spell.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"11\" data-roll-max=\"12\">11-12</td><td class=\"col-11\">Roll a [[/r d10]]. Your height changes by a number of inches equal to the roll. If the roll is odd, you shrink. If the roll is even, you grow.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"13\" data-roll-max=\"14\">13-14</td><td class=\"col-11\">You cast @spell[confusion] centered on yourself.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"15\" data-roll-max=\"16\">15-16</td><td class=\"col-11\">For the next minute, you regain 5 hit points at the start of each of your turns.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"17\" data-roll-max=\"18\">17-18</td><td class=\"col-11\">You grow a long beard made of feathers that remains until you sneeze, at which point the feathers explode out from your face.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"19\" data-roll-max=\"20\">19-20</td><td class=\"col-11\">You cast @spell[grease] centered on yourself.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"21\" data-roll-max=\"22\">21-22</td><td class=\"col-11\">Creatures have disadvantage on saving throws against the next spell you cast in the next minute that involves a saving throw.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"23\" data-roll-max=\"24\">23-24</td><td class=\"col-11\">Your skin turns a vibrant shade of blue. A @spell[remove curse] spell can end this effect.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"25\" data-roll-max=\"26\">25-26</td><td class=\"col-11\">An eye appears on your forehead for the next minute. During that time, you have advantage on Wisdom (@skill[Perception]) checks that rely on sight.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"27\" data-roll-max=\"28\">27-28</td><td class=\"col-11\">For the next minute, all your spells with a casting time of 1 action have a casting time of 1 bonus action.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"29\" data-roll-max=\"30\">29-30</td><td class=\"col-11\">You teleport up to 60 feet to an unoccupied space of your choice that you can see.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"31\" data-roll-max=\"32\">31-32</td><td class=\"col-11\">You are transported to the Astral Plane until the end of your next turn, after which time you return to the space you previously occupied or the nearest unoccupied space if that space is occupied.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"33\" data-roll-max=\"34\">33-34</td><td class=\"col-11\">Maximize the damage of the next damaging spell you cast within the next minute.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"35\" data-roll-max=\"36\">35-36</td><td class=\"col-11\">Roll a [[/r d10]]. Your age changes by a number of years equal to the roll. If the roll is odd, you get younger (minimum 1 year old). If the roll is even, you get older.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"37\" data-roll-max=\"38\">37-38</td><td class=\"col-11\">[[/r 1d6]] @creature[flumph||flumphs] controlled by the DM appear in unoccupied spaces within 60 feet of you and are @condition[frightened] of you. They vanish after 1 minute.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"39\" data-roll-max=\"40\">39-40</td><td class=\"col-11\">You regain [[/r 2d10]] hit points.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"41\" data-roll-max=\"42\">41-42</td><td class=\"col-11\">You turn into a potted plant until the start of your next turn. While a plant, you are @condition[incapacitated] and have vulnerability to all damage. If you drop to 0 hit points, your pot breaks, and your form reverts.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"43\" data-roll-max=\"44\">43-44</td><td class=\"col-11\">For the next minute, you can teleport up to 20 feet as a bonus action on each of your turns.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"45\" data-roll-max=\"46\">45-46</td><td class=\"col-11\">You cast @spell[levitate] on yourself.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"47\" data-roll-max=\"48\">47-48</td><td class=\"col-11\">A @creature[unicorn] controlled by the DM appears in a space within 5 feet of you, then disappears 1 minute later.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"49\" data-roll-max=\"50\">49-50</td><td class=\"col-11\">You can't speak for the next minute. Whenever you try, pink bubbles float out of your mouth.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"51\" data-roll-max=\"52\">51-52</td><td class=\"col-11\">A spectral shield hovers near you for the next minute, granting you a +2 bonus to AC and immunity to @spell[magic missile].</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"53\" data-roll-max=\"54\">53-54</td><td class=\"col-11\">You are immune to being intoxicated by alcohol for the next [[/r 5d6]] days.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"55\" data-roll-max=\"56\">55-56</td><td class=\"col-11\">Your hair falls out but grows back within 24 hours.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"57\" data-roll-max=\"58\">57-58</td><td class=\"col-11\">For the next minute, any flammable object you touch that isn't being worn or carried by another creature bursts into flame.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"59\" data-roll-max=\"60\">59-60</td><td class=\"col-11\">You regain your lowest-level expended spell slot.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"61\" data-roll-max=\"62\">61-62</td><td class=\"col-11\">For the next minute, you must shout when you speak.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"63\" data-roll-max=\"64\">63-64</td><td class=\"col-11\">You cast @spell[fog cloud] centered on yourself.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"65\" data-roll-max=\"66\">65-66</td><td class=\"col-11\">Up to three creatures you choose within 30 feet of you take [[/r 4d10]] lightning damage.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"67\" data-roll-max=\"68\">67-68</td><td class=\"col-11\">You are @condition[frightened] by the nearest creature until the end of your next turn.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"69\" data-roll-max=\"70\">69-70</td><td class=\"col-11\">Each creature within 30 feet of you becomes @condition[invisible] for the next minute. The invisibility ends on a creature when it attacks or casts a spell.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"71\" data-roll-max=\"72\">71-72</td><td class=\"col-11\">You gain resistance to all damage for the next minute.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"73\" data-roll-max=\"74\">73-74</td><td class=\"col-11\">A random creature within 60 feet of you becomes @condition[poisoned] for [[/r 1d4]] hours.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"75\" data-roll-max=\"76\">75-76</td><td class=\"col-11\">You glow with bright light in a 30-foot radius for the next minute. Any creature that ends its turn within 5 feet of you is @condition[blinded] until the end of its next turn.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"77\" data-roll-max=\"78\">77-78</td><td class=\"col-11\">You cast @spell[polymorph] on yourself. If you fail the saving throw, you turn into a sheep for the spell's duration.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"79\" data-roll-max=\"80\">79-80</td><td class=\"col-11\">Illusory butterflies and flower petals flutter in the air within 10 feet of you for the next minute.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"81\" data-roll-max=\"82\">81-82</td><td class=\"col-11\">You can take one additional action immediately.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"83\" data-roll-max=\"84\">83-84</td><td class=\"col-11\">Each creature within 30 feet of you takes [[/r 1d10]] necrotic damage. You regain hit points equal to the sum of the necrotic damage dealt.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"85\" data-roll-max=\"86\">85-86</td><td class=\"col-11\">You cast @spell[mirror image].</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"87\" data-roll-max=\"88\">87-88</td><td class=\"col-11\">You cast @spell[fly] on a random creature within 60 feet of you.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"89\" data-roll-max=\"90\">89-90</td><td class=\"col-11\">You become @condition[invisible] for the next minute. During that time, other creatures can't hear you. The invisibility ends if you attack or cast a spell.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"91\" data-roll-max=\"92\">91-92</td><td class=\"col-11\">If you die within the next minute, you immediately come back to life as if by the @spell[reincarnate] spell.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"93\" data-roll-max=\"94\">93-94</td><td class=\"col-11\">Your size increases by one size category for the next minute.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"95\" data-roll-max=\"96\">95-96</td><td class=\"col-11\">You and all creatures within 30 feet of you gain vulnerability to piercing damage for the next minute.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"97\" data-roll-max=\"98\">97-98</td><td class=\"col-11\">You are surrounded by faint, ethereal music for the next minute.</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-1 text-center\" data-roll-min=\"99\" data-roll-max=\"100\">99-00</td><td class=\"col-11\">You regain all expended sorcery points.</td></tr></tbody></table></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"turn"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["4d10","lightning"],["1d10","necrotic"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Sorcerer 1 (Wild)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"PHB","hash":"wild%20magic%20surge_sorcerer_phb_wild_phb_1_phb","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"912af75d89cea91471ba0c5ebf11f62f6ac124c4"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682005698045,"modifiedTime":1682005698045,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"TKLhvXZFbva2psD0"}
{"name":"Restore Balance","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p><i>1st-level Clockwork Soul feature</i></p><p>Your connection to the plane of absolute order allows you to equalize chaotic moments. When a creature you can see within 60 feet of you is about to roll a [[/r d20]] with advantage or disadvantage, you can use your reaction to prevent the roll from being affected by advantage and disadvantage.</p><p>You can use this feature a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus, and you regain all expended uses when you finish a long rest.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":"When a creature you can see within 60 feet of you is about to roll a d20 with advantage or disadvantage, you can use"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"@prof","per":"lr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Sorcerer 1 (Clockwork Soul)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"adnd5e":{"itemInfo":{"type":"reaction"}},"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"TCE","hash":"restore%20balance_sorcerer_phb_clockwork%20soul_tce_1_tce","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"8e05be452fa3798fce038ea675b9e5f81856f32a"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682005699702,"modifiedTime":1682005699702,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"TXWLafVnDJoikm4C"