{"name":"Sunlit Path","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>The world, illuminated and revealed by summer's long days, becomes easier for you to traverse. Beginning at 6th level, your walking speed increases by 15 feet, and you gain resistance to radiant damage.</p><p>Additionally, when calculating your overland travel pace for 1 minute, 1 mile, and 1 day, your speed and the speed of any allies you choose within 30 feet of you increases by 100 feet per minute, 1 mile per hour, and 6 miles per day.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Ar2","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Sorcerer 6 (Sun Bloodline)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"Ar2","hash":"sunlit%20path_sorcerer_phb_sun%20bloodline_ar2_6_ar2","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"346874d9ea56760baba24615bcd1ff7245976c1e"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682005694980,"modifiedTime":1682005694980,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"mnJ5yZlKUGg8RzZw"}
{"name":"Pyromancer's Fury","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>Starting at 14th level, when you are hit by a melee attack, you can use your reaction to deal fire damage to the attacker. The damage equals your sorcerer level, and ignores resistance to fire damage.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PSK","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":"when you are hit by a melee attack, you can use"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Sorcerer 14 (Pyromancer (PSK))","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"adnd5e":{"itemInfo":{"type":"reaction"}},"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"PSK","hash":"pyromancer's%20fury_sorcerer_phb_pyromancer%20(psk)_psk_14_psk","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"70fe488357d5198b97d10efd3591ba4d2acf6b1d"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682005698671,"modifiedTime":1682005698671,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"n9N4YOj0yG9Zx71o"}
{"name":"Manifest Inscriptions","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>At 6th level, you can reveal hidden glyphs and enchantments that surround you. As an action, you can expend a charged rune to cause any hidden magical marks, runes, wards, or glyphs within 15 feet of you to reveal themselves with a glow for 1 round. This glow is considered dim light for a 5 foot radius around the mark or glyph.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TDCS","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Sorcerer 6 (Runechild)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"TalDorei","hash":"manifest%20inscriptions_sorcerer_phb_runechild_taldorei_6_taldorei","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"f553647ccb7b602a1e5d7ce9346e37b29189a778"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682005695566,"modifiedTime":1682005695566,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"nGTSA2WkKRLpZNHN"}
{"name":"Umbral Form","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>Starting at 18th level, you can spend 6 sorcery points as a bonus action to magically transform yourself into a shadowy form. In this form, you have resistance to all damage except force and radiant damage, and you can move through other creatures and objects as if they were difficult terrain. You take 5 force damage if you end your turn inside an object.</p><p>You remain in this form for 1 minute. It ends early if you are @condition[incapacitated], if you die, or if you dismiss it as a bonus action.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["5","force"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Sorcerer 18 (Shadow)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"XGE","hash":"umbral%20form_sorcerer_phb_shadow_xge_18_xge","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"3bba3ca82c4aed7ab9e46e2fa459774730a99048"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682005701486,"modifiedTime":1682005701486,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"nmjId10SYBjE7XjG"}
